Nadidisappoint ako...
Kasi nagsinungaling ka saamin.
Maya quietly lowers her head.
[signal arg="emotion_persist:sad:2"]
She doesn't answer.
Bakit ang hirap mong pagkatiwalaan ngayon?
The words linger.
No one speaks.
[background arg="res://Art/Backgrounds/campus_hallway.png" fade="0.7"]
Maya walks alone.
Students pass by laughing.
Talking about projects.
Graduation.
Internships.
She keeps walking.
Without looking at anyone.
